OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775462699
OL,3,CManslaughter charge after man dies 24
OL,4,Chours after altercation
OL,6,FA man has been charged with
OL,7,Fmanslaughter after another died
OL,8,Ffollowing an altercation 24 hours
OL,9,Fearlier.
OL,11,FMarek Krygier, 35, suffered a head
OL,12,Finjury after it is believed he was
OL,13,Finvolved in an incident with two men
OL,14,Foutside of Home Bargains in Byrom
OL,15,FStreet, in Blackburn, at around 6.45pm
OL,16,Fon 27 March.
OL,18,FHe later collapsed and was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital where he died the following
OL,20,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
