PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775462699
OL,3,CManslaughter charge after man dies 24
OL,4,Chours after altercation
OL,6,FLancashire Police says despite
OL,7,Fextensive enquiries it has been unable
OL,8,Fto trace any family of Marek, a Polish
OL,9,Fnational, and is urging anyone with
OL,10,Finformation for come forward.
OL,12,FTwo men, aged 43 and 44 from
OL,13,FBlackburn, were arrested on 31 March
OL,14,Fon suspicion of murder.
OL,16,FConnor Doyle, 43, of Cheltenham Road,
OL,17,FBlackburn, has since been charged with
OL,18,Fmanslaughter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
