OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775462699
OL,3,CManslaughter charge after man dies 24
OL,4,Chours after altercation
OL,6,FThe 44-year-old man has been released
OL,7,Fon condition bail pending the result
OL,8,Fof further enquiries.
OL,10,FOfficers say they are keen to hear
OL,11,Ffrom anyone who visited Home Bargains
OL,12,Fbetween 4pm and 9pm on 27 March and
OL,13,Fwho witnessed the altercation between
OL,14,Fa group of men outside the main
OL,15,Fentrance.
OL,17,FThey are also asking for anyone with
OL,18,Ffootage - including dashcam, CCTV or
OL,19,Fmobile phone, to get in touch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
